{"metadata":{"kernelspec":{"display_name":"Python 3","language":"python","name":"python3"},"language_info":{"name":"python","version":"3.12.12","mimetype":"text/x-python","codemirror_mode":{"name":"ipython","version":3},"pygments_lexer":"ipython3","nbconvert_exporter":"python","file_extension":".py"},"colab":{"provenance":[]},"kaggle":{"accelerator":"nvidiaTeslaT4","dataSources":[],"dockerImageVersionId":31329,"isInternetEnabled":true,"language":"python","sourceType":"notebook","isGpuEnabled":true}},"nbformat_minor":5,"nbformat":4,"cells":[{"id":"64d164d7","cell_type":"markdown","source":"# DeepSeek 7B + Anthropic HH Steering Vector on Kaggle GPU\n\nFresh notebook for computing and applying a steering vector with a DeepSeek 7B chat model on Kaggle.\n\nPipeline:\n\n`HH dataset -> chosen/rejected pairs -> hidden states -> steering vector -> safe hook -> evaluation`\n","metadata":{}},{"id":"fcef1423","cell_type":"markdown","source":"## 1. Kaggle runtime checklist\n\nBefore running:\n\n- Enable `Internet`\n- Set `Accelerator` to `GPU`\n- Add a Kaggle secret named `HF_TOKEN` for authenticated Hugging Face downloads\n- This notebook is designed for a 7B chat model loaded in full 16-bit precision on Kaggle GPU","metadata":{}},{"id":"89066860","cell_type":"code","source":"!pip -q install -U transformers datasets accelerate sentencepiece huggingface_hub","metadata":{"trusted":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-04-18T14:59:54.604064Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-04-18T14:59:54.604363Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-04-18T15:00:16.286088Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2026-04-18T14:59:54.604332Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-04-18T15:00:16.285211Z"}},"outputs":[{"name":"stdout","text":"\u001b[2K   \u001b[90m鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣\u001b[0m \u001b[32m10.2/10.2 MB\u001b[0m \u001b[31m71.3 MB/s\u001b[0m eta \u001b[36m0:00:00\u001b[0m:00:01\u001b[0m:01\u001b[0m\n\u001b[2K   \u001b[90m鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲攣鈹佲